			<Item class="Script" referent="RBXD8716EF6854A4885817732AAD2C74030">
				<Properties>
					<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--[[ 

(( 𝙎𝙆𝙔𝙩𝙚𝙘𝙝 𝘢𝘦𝘳𝘰𝘔𝘪𝘯𝘪 ))

Kit: https://create.roblox.com/store/asset/95655420322952/SKYtech-aeroMini
Source Module: https://create.roblox.com/store/asset/100312192466174/aeroMini-Source-Module

( 𝗜𝗠𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧𝗔𝗡𝗧 )
- The source module (aeroMini Source) can be placed only once in workspace.
- It is recommended to only put one source module in your games. Only duplicate it into
aircraft models if you insert them with admin command in places where aircraft isn't
the primary content.
- It is also recommended to opt-in for the cloud update if you want to avoid duplicating
the source module. Join the community server (13+) to get the cloud version.

( 𝗜𝗻𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗹𝗹𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 )
[Optional] Delete ThumbnailCamera and "READ ME" (this script) when you are done reading.
- Add aircraft parts inside the Body or Main, or any location you desire to.
- To add animations, or exclude parts from the aircraft weld, add a WeldConstraint, name it
"IgnoreWeld" and place inside the part/model you want to ignore. You will need to make your
own animation and weld scripts.
- Adjust the settings to your liking and it is completed.

( 𝘉𝘶𝘪𝘭𝘵-𝘪𝘯 𝘮𝘰𝘥𝘪𝘧𝘪𝘤𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯𝘴 )
The kit has included built-in mods which can be modified or removed.
- Anti-jump for Pilot Seat
- Group Lock
- Sound Handler
- Flight Instruments
- Control Guide
- Mobile Control Module

aeroMini has nearly the same setup as the aeroLite, meaning some mods can be used together.

* 𝘏𝘢𝘷𝘦 𝘧𝘶𝘯 𝘧𝘭𝘺𝘪𝘯𝘨 *

]]
]]></ProtectedString>
